        "exp_laundry_yQQrGN": {
          "type": "exp-laundry",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow_text": "",
            "title": "less impact on the planet",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "Fast fashion has taken a serious toll on the planet. And even many “sustainable” garments break down quickly because of frequent washing.\n\nBy reducing the need to wash your clothes, we also reduce how often they need to be replaced. Fewer washes and longer-lasting garments mean less clothing waste, lower overconsumption, reduced detergent and chemical pollution, and less water wasted over time.",
