            "eyebrow_text": "04 — Buy less. Replace less.",
            "title": "Reducing Overconsumption",
            "description": "HercLéon supports a more minimal way of dressing: fewer pieces, worn more often, replaced less frequently. That means less overconsumption, fewer items needed overall, and clothing that fits naturally into travel and everyday life.",
